# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

## [Unreleased] - 2025-01-20

### Added
- 📱 **FAQ Page**: Complete FAQ screen with 10 common questions and answers
- 🌐 **FAQ Translations**: Full English and Spanish localization for FAQ content
- 🎯 **FAQ Access**: New FAQ button in drawer menu with help icon
- 📐 **Window Size**: Default app window size set to 600x950px for better mobile experience
- ➕ **Larger Add Icon**: Increased "Add Stage" button size from 24px to 32px in process creation

### Enhanced
- 🔵 **Improved Dots**: Changed dots indicator to always show filled circles (solid colored)
- ⭐ **Improved Stars**: Changed stars indicator to always show filled stars (solid colored)  
- 🎯 **Better Numbers**: Improved number centering in circular indicators with better text alignment
- 📏 **Number Container**: Increased number indicator size from 24x24 to 26x26 pixels

### Fixed
- 🐛 **Text Corruption**: Reviewed and verified no corrupted text remains in codebase

### Technical
- 🏗️ **Architecture**: Added FAQScreen widget with ExpansionTile components
- 🔧 **Localization**: Extended ARB files with 23 new translation keys
- 📱 **UI Components**: Enhanced process indicators with better visual styling
- 🎨 **Visual Polish**: Improved stage indicator consistency across all styles